WEBVTT

00:00:00.619 --> 00:00:02.081
geforn keyn

00:00:02.053 --> 00:00:03.363
BERGEN B-

00:00:02.138 --> 00:00:03.651
BERGEN BELSEN

00:00:03.707 --> 00:00:06.097
vi azoy

00:00:06.390 --> 00:00:08.358
zent ir dort ongekumen?

00:00:08.196 --> 00:00:10.468
ze'mir ongekumen vider mit a tsug

00:00:10.474 --> 00:00:13.471
vider arayngeleygt ale mit di vagonen

00:00:13.714 --> 00:00:16.205
gornisht, m'hot ⟨undz mitgegebn⟩ a deke.

00:00:16.853 --> 00:00:21.470
a deke hobn zey undz mitgegebn. keyn esn hot men gornisht mitgegebn,

00:00:22.084 --> 00:00:23.833
m'hot gezogt vu me geyt?

00:00:23.738 --> 00:00:27.565
neyn, gornisht gezogt vu me geyt. m'iz geforn, ⟨vayl mir⟩

00:00:27.565 --> 00:00:33.182
a ful tsug iz gevezn on a benkl, on a gornisht. m'hot zikh alts gezets oyf der erd.

00:00:33.222 --> 00:00:38.349
un azoy iz men gezesn, biz m'iz dort aro- ahingekumen. dos zi gevezn a lange rayze

00:00:38.349 --> 00:00:40.573
vayl dos iz fun Poyln

00:00:40.765 --> 00:00:42.362
biz keyn Daytshland.

00:00:43.347 --> 00:00:44.229
di

00:00:43.347 --> 00:00:45.653
vi lang iz men azoy geforn?

00:00:44.229 --> 00:00:47.491
dos ken ikh nisht zogn. s'iz gevezn zikher a tsvey vokhn.

00:00:47.717 --> 00:00:49.910
un m'hot zikh opgeshtelt in mitn?

00:00:49.168 --> 00:00:51.560
in tsvishn, zey hobn zikh opgeshtelt

00:00:51.560 --> 00:00:57.260
un hot tsu undz gegebn a shtikele broyt. ikh veys nisht tsi gegebn dem tsveytn tsi UNK tog ken ikh nisht UNK erinen

00:00:57.260 --> 00:00:59.760
un a bisele vaser, un azoy iz men gevezn f-

00:00:59.833 --> 00:01:00.569
geforn.

00:00:59.833 --> 00:01:02.679
s'iz do mentshn vos zenen antlofn fun dort?

00:01:02.668 --> 00:01:04.293
ikh gleyb nisht. neyn.

00:01:04.293 --> 00:01:05.391
ikh gleyb nisht.

00:01:05.391 --> 00:01:09.227
gleyb nisht, vayl ze'mir gevezn bloyz froyen. s'iz nisht gevezn keyn mener.

00:01:09.368 --> 00:01:11.859
mener iz gevezn ⟨SPRITLER⟩ vi froyen

00:01:12.338 --> 00:01:14.019
kh'gleyb nisht zenen antlofn.

00:01:12.861 --> 00:01:15.167
un kinder zenen geven?

00:01:14.262 --> 00:01:18.508
neyn. s'iz shoyn nisht gevezn keyn kind, nebekh. FINISHED, s'iz nisht gevezn keyn kind.

00:01:19.071 --> 00:01:20.910
nisht gevezn keyn eyn kind.

00:01:20.910 --> 00:01:25.070
di ungarishe vos zenen gekumen UNK mit di kinder hot men band ⟨sekurirt⟩. OSWIECIM iz

00:01:25.070 --> 00:01:26.870
bald nisht arayngeganen keyn kind.

00:01:27.103 --> 00:01:28.936
keyn eyn kind nisht gevezn.

00:01:28.369 --> 00:01:30.320
un mit aykh iz geven

00:01:30.445 --> 00:01:31.300
ver?

00:01:31.221 --> 00:01:34.438
di mame iz gevezn shoyn letstn mit mir di gantse tsayt.

00:01:34.562 --> 00:01:37.795
di shvester iz shoyn nisht gevezn, iz gevezn in RAVENSBRUCK

00:01:37.795 --> 00:01:42.167
un nor ikh mit di mame. der tate iz oykhet nisht gevezn

00:01:42.173 --> 00:01:44.597
un der tate iz, azoy vi undz ze'mir

00:01:44.687 --> 00:01:46.436
avek fun PLASZOW

00:01:46.746 --> 00:01:50.824
hot er gevust ze'mir nishto, un er hot dokh shver un biter gearbet

00:01:51.083 --> 00:01:54.240
hot er shoyn gezogt "ikh vil shoyn nisht blaybn in PLASZOW."

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:57.670
⟨ven⟩ gekumen der ershter transport, hot er zikh shoyn tsugeshtelt

00:01:57.850 --> 00:02:00.274
un der transport iz geganen keyn MAUTHAUSEN

00:02:00.887 --> 00:02:03.631
un dort iz er gevezn leyder nisht lang

00:02:04.633 --> 00:02:07.512
iz er gevezn, un hot gearbet

00:02:07.570 --> 00:02:13.034
vayl mayn onkl iz dort oykhet gevezn, hot er undz fartseylt, un hot gearbet, s'iz gevezn azolkhe netsn

00:02:13.034 --> 00:02:20.965
un zamd mit shteyner, ot azoy az di shteyner zenen geblibn. di sht- der zamd iz adurkhgeforn, un di shteyner zenen geblibn. yednfal

00:02:20.965 --> 00:02:23.780
oyf dem iz er gesh- dos hot er gearbet

00:02:24.006 --> 00:02:28.775
un hot gekrign nebekh tifus, un ⟨zi⟩ iz nebekh dort avekge⟨UNK⟩ in MAUTHAUSEN.

00:02:29.541 --> 00:02:32.336
ven zent ir ongekumen in BERGEN BELSEN?

00:02:32.292 --> 00:02:38.968
ze'mir ongekumen vintertsayt. s'iz gevezn zeyer, zeyer kalt. vintertsayt zenen mir gekumen in BERGEN BELSEN.

00:02:39.025 --> 00:02:43.097
es hot geregnt, gegosn demolts. undz ho'mir nisht gekrign keyn

00:02:43.097 --> 00:02:47.136
keyn barakn, azoy vi in OSWIECIM, nor TENTn

00:02:47.142 --> 00:02:51.473
un m'hot undz gegebn a sh- aza bintl ho- shtroy

00:02:51.597 --> 00:02:55.270
yedn eynem in di hant arayn, un dos hot geheysn di bet.

00:02:55.410 --> 00:03:01.625
undz ho'mir undz geleygt oyf di erd. undz ho'mir undz arayngeleygt in a TENT arayn, vifl mentshn veys ikh, gevezn ful.

00:03:01.625 --> 00:03:03.656
m'iz gelegn azoy vi fish

00:03:03.747 --> 00:03:06.376
eyner do mitn kop, eyner do mit di fis

00:03:06.376 --> 00:03:09.799
un azoy iz men gelegn dortn, azoy geshlofn, a tsayt.

00:03:08.742 --> 00:03:10.862
vi zent ir geven ongetun?

00:03:11.121 --> 00:03:21.729
 ze'mir gevezn ongetun m- in a, m- in a, nisht afile mit a ⟨pashak⟩, nor a bluzke zenen mir gevezn, a bluzke mit a rok, un dos iz gevezn, on a shka- gornisht, vintertsayt, azoy iz men geganen.

00:03:21.499 --> 00:03:22.252
shikh?

00:03:22.697 --> 00:03:30.845
shikh hot men gekrign dort in OSWIECIM hobn zey gegebn azolkhene holtserne shikh, vayl eygene shikh hobn zey tsugenumen, hobn zey gegen holtserne shikh in OSWIECIM

00:03:30.845 --> 00:03:33.306
un mit dem zenen mir geganen keyn BERGEN BELSEN.

00:03:33.295 --> 00:03:35.640
un vos hot men dort getun?

00:03:34.746 --> 00:03:39.364
gornisht. a gantse tsayt gornisht getun, un shpeter iz gekumen

00:03:39.589 --> 00:03:42.215
vintertsayt, iz gekumen vintn

00:03:42.458 --> 00:03:46.648
un s'iz gekumen zeyer a groyse regn, un bay nakht oyf eyn mol

00:03:46.648 --> 00:03:49.083
ale tseltn faln arunter.

00:03:49.782 --> 00:03:58.562
hot men undz ale genumen. yeder hot gekhapt dos shtikele, di deke mit dem shtikl holts iz shoy- iz dos shtroy iz gornisht gevezn, vayl s'iz gevezn nas

00:03:58.562 --> 00:04:00.207
nor di deke hot men gehat

00:04:00.207 --> 00:04:02.398
un m'hot undz gefirt in a kokh arayn.

00:04:02.556 --> 00:04:06.280
un shpeter in andern tog hot men undz shoyn gefirt in a barak arayn

00:04:07.078 --> 00:04:10.686
azoy az ze'mir shoyn sh- shlofn oyf a n- oyf a pritshe

00:04:10.686 --> 00:04:15.341
o- on a gornisht, nisht keyn shtroy, nisht gorn- nor a shtikl holts, azoy ze'mir geshlofn.

00:04:14.571 --> 00:04:17.029
vos far a sort lager iz dos geven?

00:04:17.338 --> 00:04:24.504
dos iz oykhet gevezn nisht keyn ARBEITS lager. dos iz gevezn a katset lager, vos oykhet hot gevart nemen mentshn vayter.

00:04:24.831 --> 00:04:27.035
vos far a sort mentshn zenen geven?

00:04:25.658 --> 00:04:28.346
dort zenen gevezn mentshn tsufelik

00:04:28.346 --> 00:04:34.109
dos hob ikh shpeter gevust f- demolts vu undz ho'mir dort in OSWIEZCIM ho'mir nisht gevust, vayl zenen gekumen mentshn a sakh

00:04:34.109 --> 00:04:36.429
vos hobn gehat fremde papirn

00:04:36.429 --> 00:04:43.354
zenen geblibn dort in, in, UNK ABER undz ho'mir nisht UNK vayl dos UNK gevezn zeyer groys. eyner fun tsveytn hot gornisht gevust

00:04:43.512 --> 00:04:45.302
dos hot men shpeter gevor-

00:04:45.302 --> 00:04:48.372
shpeter fun THERESIENSTADT hot men gebrengt dort zeyer

00:04:48.372 --> 00:04:51.785
di mentshn vos zenen glaykh fun Tshekhn ⟨do⟩ arayngekumen

00:04:51.785 --> 00:04:57.376
hot men zey oykhet dort gebrengt ahin. ver hot gevust? keyner hot nisht gevust. yeder hot zikh gehaltn mit zayn barak.

00:04:57.147 --> 00:04:59.098
un esn hot men gegebn?

00:04:58.885 --> 00:05:03.131
NO, dos zelbe m- PORTION vos in OSWIECIM. a shtikele broyt un a zup.

00:05:03.222 --> 00:05:06.390
un ver hot, ver iz geven di oyfzeers dort?

00:05:05.719 --> 00:05:07.890
S.S. manen, alts S.S. manen.

00:05:08.335 --> 00:05:11.063
un SELKTIONEN iz geven?

00:05:10.157 --> 00:05:15.618
neyn, nor tsu di arbet hobn zey genumen. dort nisht gevezn keyn kremator- efsher iz gevezn. ikh hob nisht gevust.

00:05:15.878 --> 00:05:16.810
un

00:05:15.895 --> 00:05:18.521
undz ho'mir nisht gevust. s'iz eyn mol gekumen a

00:05:18.544 --> 00:05:19.736
a yeke

00:05:20.451 --> 00:05:22.706
un hot gedarft finef hundert mentshn

00:05:24.602 --> 00:05:26.385
hot er

00:05:26.813 --> 00:05:33.023
er hot nisht gekukt oyfn plats fun vi azoy der mentsh, vi m- der mentsh zet oys, un tsi ⟨zi⟩ hot koyekh tsu arbetn

00:05:33.023 --> 00:05:34.603
un hot gekukt oyf di hent.

00:05:35.503 --> 00:05:37.741
ikh hob gehat zeyer mogere hent

00:05:38.187 --> 00:05:40.453
hot er mikh avekgeshtelt. di mame hot mi-

00:05:40.453 --> 00:05:41.488
genumen

00:05:41.612 --> 00:05:46.449
un azoy vi ikh hob gezen az mikh hot men avekgeshtelt, hob ikh ⟨hintn⟩ UNK tsugeganen tsu di mame.

00:05:46.573 --> 00:05:48.187
ikh bin nokh mitgeganen

00:05:48.868 --> 00:05:50.515
mitgeganen mit di mame.

00:05:50.809 --> 00:05:52.760
un vu iz men gegangen?

00:05:52.125 --> 00:05:54.144
m'iz geganen keyn ASCHERSLEBEN.

00:05:55.281 --> 00:05:59.038
in ASCHERSLEBEN hot men, hot men undz gebrengt

00:05:59.432 --> 00:06:02.162
dort iz gevezn a munitsyon fabrik

00:06:02.162 --> 00:06:03.577
bay FLUGZEUGE

00:06:04.123 --> 00:06:08.363
dort frier, dort vu undz hot men gegebn di barakn hobn gevoynt yekes

00:06:08.363 --> 00:06:11.653
nor y- zey, di yekes, hot men genumen in front arayn

00:06:11.653 --> 00:06:13.651
hot men undz gegebn

00:06:13.995 --> 00:06:17.887
di barakn, un undz ze'mir gearbet, tog SCHICHTE un nakht SCHICHTE.

00:06:18.012 --> 00:06:19.963
in ASCHERSLEBEN

00:06:19.307 --> 00:06:20.860
in ASCHERSLEBEN, yo.

00:06:20.860 --> 00:06:22.143
bay di amunitsye.

00:06:22.143 --> 00:06:27.017
fun, fun eyn zayt iz geshtanen der yeke, a yeke iz geshtanen, a DEUTSCHER

00:06:27.090 --> 00:06:31.606
un hot arayngeshosn, un ikh bin geshtanen fun tsveyte zayt

00:06:31.866 --> 00:06:33.002
mit a

00:06:33.002 --> 00:06:34.340
tsen kilo

00:06:34.414 --> 00:06:37.901
un dos gehaltn mit aza koyekh, zol dos vern PLAT.

00:06:38.262 --> 00:06:44.432
di shroyf vos er shist arayn hot gedarft vern PLAT, un ikh bin geshtanen mitn gantsn t- koyekh a gantsn tog

00:06:44.539 --> 00:06:47.418
un az, er hot arayngeshosn, hin un tsurik.

00:06:47.685 --> 00:06:49.045
vos iz

00:06:48.015 --> 00:06:52.886
un gemakht, dos iz di FLUGZEUGE, di PL- di shtiker fun FLUGZEUGE makht men azoy

00:06:53.601 --> 00:06:59.080
nu, vos undz flien mir yetst, mit di, dos makht men azoy a FLUGZEU- sh- tsvey mentshn shteyen. eyner shteyt fun eyn zayt

00:06:59.080 --> 00:07:02.980
zol nisht zayn keyn luft. dos muzt z- hot zikh gemuzt oyfmakhn di, di shroyf

00:07:02.980 --> 00:07:05.258
oyf eyn zayt, zol nisht araynkumen keyn luft

00:07:05.258 --> 00:07:10.082
un ikh bin gevezn dos groyse giber, un ikh bin geshtanen azoy mit tsen kilo a gantsn tog.

00:07:10.594 --> 00:07:13.490
un ikh hob gehat nakht SCHICHTE, hob ikh geshtanen a gantse nakht.

00:07:14.104 --> 00:07:17.608
un m'hot dortn beser ge- ⟨VERFLIEGT⟩ di mentshn?

00:07:16.129 --> 00:07:19.869
z- dos zelbe gevezn, dos zelbe, dos zelbe.

00:07:18.643 --> 00:07:22.231
un ver hot dort oyfgepast? ver iz geven der oyfzeer?

00:07:20.938 --> 00:07:27.007
S.S. manen. dort gevezn S.S. manen. gevezn S.S. mankes oykhet. di froyen zenen oykhet gevezn.

00:07:27.250 --> 00:07:31.229
der S.S. man takesh vos iz geshtanen bay mir, ikh bin dort gevezn a kind

00:07:31.229 --> 00:07:33.605
hot yeder gehat mit mir rakhmones

00:07:33.966 --> 00:07:35.916
iz geganen der S.S. man.

00:07:35.916 --> 00:07:39.126
a sakh mol hot men arayngeleygt a shtikele broyt

00:07:39.163 --> 00:07:44.405
dort vu hot er gehat lign di ale ⟨ZUGABE⟩ tsu arbetn, hot er mir arayngeleygt a shtikele broyt.

00:07:44.580 --> 00:07:52.809
eyn mol zetst er zikh anider opruen. azoy vi er hot zikh anidergezetst opruen, hob ikh fun tsveyte zayt, hob ikh mikh oykhet gekent aniderzetsn

00:07:53.153 --> 00:07:55.183
azoy vi hob ikh mir ⟨anidergezetst in⟩

00:07:55.183 --> 00:08:02.664
bin dokh nor a mentsh, un ikh hob nisht UNK fun, fun ⟨ergets⟩ iz ongekumen a S.S. manke. zi kumt tsu mir tsu, un zi git mir a UNK fun eyn zayt

00:08:02.738 --> 00:08:06.562
a UNK fun tsveyte, UNK "vos UNKstu? vos arbetstu nisht?"

00:08:08.408 --> 00:08:10.596
biz hob ikh mikh oysgedrikt

00:08:10.652 --> 00:08:13.818
iz gevezn shoyn tsu shpet. kh'hob shoyn gekrign mayns

00:08:14.382 --> 00:08:16.091
iz der yeke tsugeganen.

00:08:16.091 --> 00:08:18.985
"du host nisht ⟨a⟩ rekhts UNK zi tsu shlogn." er hot dos gezogt.

00:08:18.985 --> 00:08:23.083
"zi iz mayn ARBEITER, un az ikh hob gezesn, hot zi gemegt zitsn.

00:08:23.545 --> 00:08:25.969
ABER yednfal, ikh hob shoyn mayns gekrign.

00:08:26.717 --> 00:08:31.819
azoy UNK vos. vi hobn zey gekhapt, azoy mentshn zenen geganen azoy arum un arum, gekukt

00:08:31.819 --> 00:08:33.759
tsi m- tsi me arbet, tsi me

00:08:33.759 --> 00:08:35.975
tsi me zitst nisht keyn minut on a arbet.

00:08:36.150 --> 00:08:39.485
un mayn mame hot oykhet dort gearbet, a gantsn UNK tog.

00:08:37.922 --> 00:08:38.878
UNK

00:08:39.441 --> 00:08:42.928
m'hot sabotirt dort? es iz geven sabotazh?

00:08:42.410 --> 00:08:44.922
sabotazh iz nisht gevezn.

00:08:44.922 --> 00:08:49.571
efsher mentshn hobn dos getun. undz ho'mir nisht, ikh hob dos do nisht getun. ikh bin geven zeyer a

00:08:49.571 --> 00:08:56.259
UNK nisht getun, vayl der yeke iz geshtanen fun y- eyn zayt UNK geshtanen di tsveyte zayt. m'hot gornisht gekent tun keyn sabotazh.

00:08:56.367 --> 00:08:59.806
bist dokh gevezn azoy oyfgepast, un arum un arum zenen geganen yekes.

00:08:59.806 --> 00:09:04.916
vi hot men gekent tun? m'hot gornisht gekent tun. un vos hobn shoyn gekent tun di finef hundert froyen? gornisht.

00:09:05.310 --> 00:09:07.931
m'hot gevust epes vos tut zikh mitn krig

00:09:07.931 --> 00:09:08.950
demolts?

00:09:09.057 --> 00:09:13.995
m'hot nisht gevust, ABER m'hot shoyn geklert, vayl di FLUGZEUGE zenen shoyn gefloygn.

00:09:14.828 --> 00:09:17.768
di FLUGZEUGE zenen shoyn gefloygn, un zey hobn shoyn

00:09:17.768 --> 00:09:22.188
zey hobn gehat planen, un zey hobn gevust az do iz a FLUGZEUG mash- fabrik

00:09:22.188 --> 00:09:25.887
zenen zey gekumen stabil oyf dem plats, un undz hot men shtabil ge-

00:09:25.887 --> 00:09:31.354
di yekes frier vu zey hobn gevoynt hobn zikh gemakht ⟨dort⟩ bunkers, hot men undz geshikt in di bunkers. far vos zog ikh

00:09:31.354 --> 00:09:34.973
az ze'mir gevorn nisht keyn mentshn nor khayes zenen mir gevorn dort?

00:09:34.973 --> 00:09:38.953
far vos? m'hot undz gevorfn, hot ges- -kumen a lyarem

00:09:39.162 --> 00:09:42.042
iz tunkl iz gevezn. m'iz gelofn in bunker arayn

00:09:42.042 --> 00:09:43.772
iz gevezn azolkhene

00:09:43.772 --> 00:09:46.440
arum un arum di vant a bret

00:09:46.440 --> 00:09:48.015
a bret tsu zitsn

00:09:48.325 --> 00:09:55.592
un ikh kum tsu geyn, ikh bin dokh gevezn shneler vi mayn mame, bin ikh gekumen tsu geyn, hot ⟨dokh⟩ ge⟨UNK⟩ UNK JEMAND zitsn. ikh hob gezen, JEMAND ligt.

00:09:55.952 --> 00:09:57.498
hob ikh gezogt "shtey oyf"

00:09:57.538 --> 00:10:02.445
zogt zi zi vil nisht. "vos heyst du vilst nisht? mayn mame ⟨do muz⟩ zitsn. ikh muz oykhet. shtey oyf."

00:10:02.445 --> 00:10:05.677
zi vil nisht oyfshteyn. hob ikh zi gekhapt bay di hor. "shtey oyf."

00:10:05.677 --> 00:10:07.179
iz zi dokh oyfgeshtanen.

00:10:07.179 --> 00:10:12.061
dos vos ⟨zi iz⟩ oyfgeshtanen iz gornisht. dem andern tog az s'iz ge- ongetsundn dos likht

00:10:12.557 --> 00:10:15.740
iz gevezn a kuzine fun di blok ALTESTE.

00:10:16.557 --> 00:10:22.558
iz zi tsugeganen tsu di blok ALTESTE, un di blok ALTESTE hot zi mikh ayngerufn. zogt zi "veyst vos do kumt dort far dir?

00:10:22.648 --> 00:10:24.779
far dir kumt dokh a shtraf dos do."

00:10:24.779 --> 00:10:29.741
mikh darf do aropshnay- ikh hob ge- koym gehat a bisele hor vos hot mir azoy fil untergevaksn.

00:10:29.741 --> 00:10:31.738
dos iz gevezn a UNK

00:10:31.812 --> 00:10:33.749
⟨vayl⟩ azoy hot zi getun. tomer hot men

00:10:33.749 --> 00:10:40.513
y- epes getun, hot zi opgeshnitn ⟨di⟩ bisele hor. ikh hob gemeynt ikh vel mikh hargenen UNK, vos zi geyt mir shoyn vider aropshnaydn di hor.

00:10:40.705 --> 00:10:44.175
tsvishn hot zi mikh, zi hot ⟨dokh⟩ gezen m'hot mit a kind tsu tun

00:10:44.282 --> 00:10:46.092
hot zi gezogt "ikh loz UNK dos

00:10:46.092 --> 00:10:50.482
loz UNK dos mol, ABER nekstes mol zolstu visn undz UNK aropgeshnitn di hor."

00:10:51.318 --> 00:10:56.358
zog ikh "vos hob ikh getun? ⟨zi hot⟩ dokh nisht gevolt mayn mame lozn zitsn, hob ikh ⟨zi gegebn⟩ a khap far di hor. ikh

00:10:56.358 --> 00:10:59.865
ikh hob gevust vu s'iz, ⟨hob ikh⟩ gekhapt bay di hor, un iz UNK oyfgeshtanen."

00:10:59.959 --> 00:11:02.315
far dem zog ikh m'iz nisht gevezn keyn mentshn.

00:11:03.030 --> 00:11:06.115
m'hot zikh yeder gevolt zayn plats, vi me zogt dos o

00:11:06.115 --> 00:11:07.665
retn, makhn.

00:11:08.008 --> 00:11:10.010
vi lang zent ir dort geven?

00:11:09.645 --> 00:11:11.844
oh, dort iz shoyn gevezn a luksus.

00:11:11.844 --> 00:11:14.620
far vos iz gevezn a luksus? vayl gevezn a pritshe

00:11:14.620 --> 00:11:21.290
un di pritshes zenen gevezn in di shtubn, UNK fun yekes in di shtubn. s'iz gevezn a prakhtike WASCHRAUM

00:11:21.290 --> 00:11:23.710
tsu vashn zikh dort hintern keler

00:11:23.710 --> 00:11:25.660
oh, dort iz gevezn ⟨shoyn⟩ a luksus

00:11:25.660 --> 00:11:29.630
dort hot men shoyn gelegn oyf di pritshes ven hot men gehat di nakht SCHICHTE bay tog

00:11:29.630 --> 00:11:34.339
hot men shoyn geklert az s'vet zayn nokh di krig vet men esn an ey, esn a shtikele broyt

00:11:34.339 --> 00:11:39.671
oy, JA, zikher, shoyn hobn a shtikl broyt tsu UNK esn. eyner hot zi gezogt "oy, ikh hob, ikh UNK ⟨eyer⟩ shpayz"

00:11:39.671 --> 00:11:42.091
un eyner hot gezogt "ikh UNK a shtikele vursht"

00:11:42.091 --> 00:11:44.331
un ikh bin gevezn azoy beyz oyf di mentshn

00:11:44.331 --> 00:11:46.261
"vos redts ets fun dem esn?

00:11:46.261 --> 00:11:51.221
vos redstu?" ikh hob nisht gekent dos fartrogn, vayl der mentsh vert dokh hungerik az me redt fun esn.

00:11:51.221 --> 00:11:52.721
"vos redts ets fun dos?"

00:11:52.721 --> 00:11:55.339
mir hobn geredt. zey hobn shoyn gekholemt

00:11:55.339 --> 00:11:56.906
az s'vet zayn dos do.

00:11:57.199 --> 00:11:59.184
vi lang zent ir dort geven?

00:11:59.106 --> 00:12:03.622
dort ze'mir shoyn gevezn a dray fir monat ze'mir dort, biz

00:12:03.763 --> 00:12:05.579
e- erev peysekh.

00:12:05.552 --> 00:12:07.486
velkhe yor iz dos geven?

00:12:05.940 --> 00:12:07.126
FEBRUARY

00:12:07.126 --> 00:12:09.427
dos iz shoyn gevezn finef un fertsik.

00:12:09.248 --> 00:12:11.857
vi alt zent ir z- geven demolts shoyn?

00:12:11.239 --> 00:12:14.085
ikh bin shoyn demolts gevezn fertsn yor.

00:12:16.740 --> 00:12:17.741
un f-

00:12:17.741 --> 00:12:20.020
f- fun dort vu ahin ⟨zent⟩

00:12:18.681 --> 00:12:23.855
undz ze'mir, iz, eyn tog zogn zey undz az me muz geyn

00:12:24.874 --> 00:12:26.066
vayter.

00:12:26.359 --> 00:12:32.563
nu, shoyn. vos geyt men? vos, m'hot dokh gornisht. me muz dokh epes organizirn. mayn mame UNK di mame

00:12:32.569 --> 00:12:34.976
iz gelofn in di kokh arayn

00:12:35.944 --> 00:12:39.650
ikh bin gevezn a kind. ikh hob shoyn azoy fil gehat fun dem shlek

00:12:39.842 --> 00:12:41.591
az ikh hob mikh nisht gevolt rirn.

00:12:41.614 --> 00:12:45.204
vu iz geganen hob ikh gez- "mame, ikh gey nisht." zi hot mikh gevolt sh-

00:12:45.204 --> 00:12:46.944
"ikh gey nisht. ikh hob shoyn genug.

00:12:47.183 --> 00:12:48.476
ikh vil nisht geyn

00:12:48.617 --> 00:12:50.973
ikh vil nisht esn, un ikh vil nisht geyn."

00:12:51.857 --> 00:12:55.327
hot zi UNK iberal geganen. iz zi gelofn in di kokh arayn

00:12:55.519 --> 00:12:58.331
un zi hot organizirt a por kartofl

00:12:59.468 --> 00:13:02.409
un azoy vi ze'mir geganen oyfn transport

00:13:02.409 --> 00:13:06.431
hobn mir dokh nisht gehat vu tsu nemen di kartofl. hobn mir gehat dem kots, di deke

00:13:06.538 --> 00:13:13.383
iz zi geganen. zi hot tsuzamgebundn, vi azoy veys ikh nisht, UNK zi hot mir gemakht a rukzak, un zi hot mir ongetun dos oyf di pleytses

00:13:14.014 --> 00:13:19.475
un ikh bin geganen ⟨ALSO⟩ dem toyte MARCH mit dem rukzak. oyf eyn mol geyt er tsu tsu mir a S.S. man

00:13:20.140 --> 00:13:22.074
zogt er "SCHMEISST DASS WEG."

00:13:22.536 --> 00:13:24.319
⟨GESAGT⟩ "ICH HABE NICHTS DORT.

00:13:24.578 --> 00:13:25.865
ikh HAB gornisht."

00:13:25.865 --> 00:13:27.755
zogt er "SCHMEISST DASS WEG"

00:13:27.755 --> 00:13:33.068
un ikh hob nisht gevolt avekshmaysn. ersht hob ikh moyre gemakht, vayl ikh hob gemakht a ganeyve. kh'hob geganvet

00:13:33.068 --> 00:13:34.148
kartofl.

00:13:34.148 --> 00:13:38.718
tsveyte hob ikh moyre gehat ⟨vel Ikh⟩ nisht hobn keyn esn untervegn, azoy hot men gegesn roye kartofl

00:13:38.718 --> 00:13:41.128
on a gornisht, bloyz a bisele roye kartofl

00:13:41.128 --> 00:13:42.898
⟨vel⟩ ikh dos oykhet nisht hobn

00:13:42.898 --> 00:13:47.083
un zi hot z- me hot gemakht pauze, zoln mir zikh kenen aniderzetsn nokh a halbn tog

00:13:47.292 --> 00:13:48.703
oyf der erd

00:13:49.165 --> 00:13:50.950
hot men zikh anidergezetst

00:13:50.950 --> 00:13:54.296
iz er tsugeganen tsu mir, un m'hot aroysgeshit di gantse kartofl.

00:13:54.296 --> 00:13:56.096
ikh hob ⟨ongehoybn⟩ tsu veynen.

00:13:56.421 --> 00:13:58.848
hot men aroysgeshit di kartofl, ABER zogt z-

00:13:58.848 --> 00:14:00.282
"HAB KEIN ANGST

00:14:00.282 --> 00:14:02.152
ikh zol dir brengen ZU esn."

00:14:02.175 --> 00:14:05.459
UND SO iz DASS gevezn. er hot mir gebrengt tsu esn.

00:14:06.192 --> 00:14:08.514
dos iz gevezn fun

00:14:07.390 --> 00:14:11.352
der TODTE marsh. der TODTE marsh vos hot geheysn di UNK

00:14:09.904 --> 00:14:12.092
fun vu iz dos gegangen?

00:14:11.352 --> 00:14:15.619
fun ASCHERSLEBEN biz THERESIENSTADT. fun Daytshland biz THERESIENSTADT.

00:14:15.152 --> 00:14:17.998
un ver iz mit aykh geven dortn?

00:14:16.975 --> 00:14:18.217
nor di mame

00:14:18.190 --> 00:14:22.386
un di gantse grupe hot men gefirt? fun di ASCHENS-

00:14:19.860 --> 00:14:22.048
nor, yo, di gantse grupe

00:14:22.054 --> 00:14:25.674
yo, der gantser finef hundert mentsh hot men zey azoy gefirt.

00:14:25.674 --> 00:14:31.984
undz ze'mir geshlofn in di stodoles. stodoles heyst vu zenen do kuen, vu zenen do ferd, dos heyst azolkhene

00:14:31.984 --> 00:14:34.079
fun holts gemakht mit shtroy.

00:14:34.079 --> 00:14:37.489
m'hot gerukt a bisele di ferd aroyf tsu di kuen

00:14:37.489 --> 00:14:39.745
un undz ze'mir geshlofn azoy oyf der erd.

00:14:38.777 --> 00:14:40.965
ver hot aykh BEGLEITET?

00:14:40.701 --> 00:14:43.732
di S.S. manen hobn undz bagla- di gantse tsayt.

00:14:42.979 --> 00:14:44.925
un mentshn zenen shoyn antlofn?

00:14:44.886 --> 00:14:46.716
neyn. m'hot gornisht antlofn.

00:14:46.716 --> 00:14:50.716
m'hot gornisht antlofn. m'hot nisht vu tsu loyfn. vu zol men dokh loyfn? zenen mir dokh ⟨baym⟩ yeke land.

00:14:50.772 --> 00:14:52.777
vu zoln mir loyfn? tsu di yekes?

00:14:51.518 --> 00:14:56.034
mentshn hobn es gezen fun di gegnt, zenen gekumen kukn?

00:14:54.420 --> 00:14:56.172
yo, zi zogt dos do.

00:14:56.172 --> 00:14:59.190
zenen aroysgeganen fun di hayzer di goyim

00:15:00.175 --> 00:15:08.609
zenen aroysgeganen fun di hayzer. ikh bin zeyer shlekht geganen, vayl ikh hob gehat a holts shikh. ikh hob nisht gekent geyn azoy, bin ikh IMMER geblibn fun hintn.

00:15:08.609 --> 00:15:16.903
di mame iz eybik geganen NACH VORNE, bay di ershte ts- tsvey rayes. di mame iz geganen, un ikh bin oykhet mit dray khavertes tsuzamen, zenen mir azoy ale dray geganen.

00:15:16.903 --> 00:15:19.979
un der ⟨S.⟩ man ⟨geshtanen⟩ do bay mir tsuzamen geganen.

00:15:20.340 --> 00:15:24.740
un, un ikh hob nisht ⟨gekent⟩ geyn, hob ikh IMMER geblibn fun hintn

00:15:24.740 --> 00:15:30.160
iz er nokhgeganen, "REGINA, REGINA, KOMM NACH VORNE, KOMM NACH VORNE."

00:15:30.229 --> 00:15:33.615
far vos hot er mikh gebetn? UNK m'hot gevust az m'iz hintn shist men.

00:15:34.735 --> 00:15:39.656
hot er gezogt "KOMM NACH VORNE, KOMM NACH VORNE," bin ikh langzam gekumen NACH VORNE.

00:15:39.460 --> 00:15:42.930
un di mentshn vos hobn

00:15:41.130 --> 00:15:44.684
un di mentshn vos zenen geblibn fun hintn, hot men zey geshosn.

00:15:44.488 --> 00:15:48.790
un di vos hobn gekukt bay di zayt hobn epes getun?

00:15:47.037 --> 00:15:52.667
yo, s'iz ge⟨UNK⟩ vos fregn zey mikh takesh, iz zi hot tsugeganen tsu a goye, vayl ikh hob nisht gekent geyn mit di shi-

00:15:52.667 --> 00:15:54.427
zol mir gebn a por shikh.

00:15:53.652 --> 00:15:55.249
ver iz tsugegangen?

00:15:54.732 --> 00:15:55.823
der yeke.

00:15:55.828 --> 00:16:00.466
tsu a yekete iz er tsugegan. "efsher HAST DU EIN PAAR SCHUHE FUR DIE KLEINES DAS meydl."

00:16:00.466 --> 00:16:04.125
⟨gezogt⟩ "ikh hob KEINE SCHUHE. vart, vart, di rusn KOMMEN shoyn NACH."

00:16:04.502 --> 00:16:05.846
HAT er GESAGT zi.

00:16:05.920 --> 00:16:10.640
shpeter zenen zey aroysgekumen kukn, er iz oykhet beyz gevezn, shoyn gevezn di ende

00:16:10.640 --> 00:16:12.960
zi hot sh- er hot shoyn oykhet gevolt antloyfn

00:16:12.960 --> 00:16:18.384
iz gevezn stabil aroysgekumen mentshn kukn. hot er gezogt "WAS SCHAUEN SIE AUF DIE SCHMUCKSTUCKEN?"

00:16:19.656 --> 00:16:23.194
zey hobn nisht geholfn? zey hobn

00:16:21.360 --> 00:16:25.510
gornisht. keyn bisele vaser hobn zey nisht gevolt gebn. gornisht.

00:16:25.510 --> 00:16:27.900
keyn por shikh hot zi nisht gevolt gebn. gornisht.

00:16:27.900 --> 00:16:29.390
er iz tsugeganen tsun ir

00:16:29.390 --> 00:16:32.289
nisht gevolt gebn keyn por shikh, un zey hobn zikher gehat.

00:16:33.308 --> 00:16:35.411
vi lang iz dos gegangen di

00:16:35.063 --> 00:16:37.335
di TODTE marsh gevezn tsvey vokhn.

00:16:37.915 --> 00:16:41.149
tsvey vokhn, tsvey vokhn. bay nakht hobn zey undz gegebn a zup

00:16:41.307 --> 00:16:44.676
mit dem shtikele broyt, un mit dem iz men azoy vayter geganen.

00:16:44.361 --> 00:16:47.257
mentshn zenen geshtorbn.

00:16:45.795 --> 00:16:48.593
OH, YES. OH, YES. a sakh mentshn zenen geshtorbn

00:16:48.593 --> 00:16:52.522
un shpeter zenen mir sh- geshtorbn vayl di ⟨layze⟩ hobn ongehoybn tsu esn.

00:16:52.883 --> 00:16:56.015
eyn mol hob ikh im gebetn zol men brengen a emer vaser

00:16:56.899 --> 00:16:59.880
vayl, shoyn bin gevezn gantse mit layz

00:17:00.578 --> 00:17:07.339
hot men gebrengt a emer vaser. du veyst vifl mentshn hobn zikh gebodn mit d- vashn dem kop mit dem emer vaser? efsher tsvontsik mentshn.

00:17:07.665 --> 00:17:13.535
alts mit ⟨di⟩ emer vaser araynges- arayngeleygt zikh ⟨in⟩ dem kop, un azoy gevashn un azoy UNK yedes dem andern.

00:17:13.535 --> 00:17:16.595
m'hot z- moyre, tomer hot men gelozt a bisele vaser oyf der erd, hot men geshrign.

00:17:17.250 --> 00:17:19.994
m'hot UNK gehat afile vu optsuvashn, tsvey vokhn.

00:17:20.423 --> 00:17:23.910
s'iz gevezn layz shoyn UNK am maystn gevezn unter di erbl.

00:17:23.933 --> 00:17:27.639
un ven, ven iz dos geven? velkhe tsayt in

00:17:26.785 --> 00:17:32.246
dos iz gevezn zumertsayt, vayl peysekh tsayt iz zumer, iz gevezn zumer, iz gevezn april, may

00:17:32.809 --> 00:17:36.026
iz gevezn. s'iz gevezn nokh sh- sheyn veter shoyn.

00:17:36.454 --> 00:17:39.840
un vu zent ir ongekumen nokh tsvey vokhn?

00:17:38.935 --> 00:17:41.932
nokh tsvey vokhn zenen mir ongekumen keyn THERESIENSTADT.

00:17:42.242 --> 00:17:43.900
vos iz dort geven?

00:17:43.322 --> 00:17:45.341
dort gevezn a lager

00:17:46.258 --> 00:17:48.001
der la- mit di

00:17:48.001 --> 00:17:53.407
s'iz nisht gevezn keyn barakn. s'iz gevezn hayzer do UNK kasernes fun militer

00:17:53.886 --> 00:17:55.365
iz es gevezn

00:17:55.557 --> 00:18:02.194
un dort hot men ale mentshn fun lager, fun, gekumen fun di lagers, fun ARBEITSLAGERS fun iberal

00:18:02.194 --> 00:18:04.072
hot men zey dort ahingebrengt

00:18:04.416 --> 00:18:08.004
un dort zenen geshtorbn poshet far tifus

00:18:08.517 --> 00:18:10.467
poshet far tifus gelegn

00:18:10.467 --> 00:18:14.587
vayl zenen shoyn gekumen untervegn, gelegn, un geshtorbn poshet far tifus.

00:18:14.997 --> 00:18:17.016
vi iz geven ayer tsushtand?

00:18:17.173 --> 00:18:24.102
mayn tsushtand nisht gevezn azoy shlekht. mayn mame's tsushtand gevezn shlekhter fun, fun mir. far vos? ikh bin gevezn zeyer moger

00:18:24.109 --> 00:18:25.757
ABER nisht gevezn krank.

00:18:25.847 --> 00:18:28.625
di mame iz gevorn krank, hot gekrign a durkhfal

00:18:29.796 --> 00:18:32.473
un zi hot zikh gegosn fun VORNE un fun hintn

00:18:33.475 --> 00:18:34.805
ABER

00:18:34.805 --> 00:18:36.877
m'hot zi langzam oysgeheylt.

00:18:36.680 --> 00:18:39.680
s'iz geven a shpitol dort?

00:18:38.250 --> 00:18:45.440
neyn, neyn. gornisht keyn shpitol. s'iz gevezn rusn zenen ongekumen, un zey zenen nisht gevezn azoy organizirt, zey ⟨zoln⟩ bald makhn a shpitol.

00:18:44.224 --> 00:18:45.950
dos iz nokh

00:18:45.950 --> 00:18:48.656
in krig, oder dos iz shoyn, ir redt fun di

00:18:47.630 --> 00:18:52.692
dos iz gevezn, zey zenen ongekumen in krig UNK di shpitol far mentshn

00:18:52.692 --> 00:18:57.109
NO, nisht gevezn keyn shpitol far, ⟨maystn⟩ nokh demolts in lager, nisht gevezn keyn shpitol

00:18:57.109 --> 00:18:59.755
un efsher iz gevez- ver hot gevolt geyn in a shpitol arayn?

00:18:59.755 --> 00:19:01.262
m'hot dokh moyre gehat.

00:19:00.981 --> 00:19:04.569
ver zenen dort geven? nor yidn in THERESIENSTADT?

00:19:03.411 --> 00:19:06.898
nor yidn, nor yidn, un yekes hobn oyfgepast.

00:19:07.275 --> 00:19:11.018
vayl zey zenen gevezn oykhet di yekes nokh in THERESIENSTADT demolts

00:19:11.018 --> 00:19:14.104
biz nokh di krig, zenen oykhet gevezn dort, di yekes.

00:19:13.198 --> 00:19:16.553
un m'hot gefilt az s'iz do a enderung bay di

00:19:16.489 --> 00:19:24.279
neyn. gornisht. geshtanen, zey hobn oyfgepast, hobn nisht gegebn tsu esn, JUSTE dos zelbe. zey hobn oyfgepast zol men nisht antloyfn, got ⟨BEHUTTE⟩.

00:19:16.553 --> 00:19:18.238
UNK di yekes?

00:19:24.825 --> 00:19:27.367
zey hobn gornisht, gornisht gehat keyn dos do.

00:19:27.542 --> 00:19:29.966
keyn enderung gevezn. alts gevezn

00:19:28.605 --> 00:19:30.776
SELEKTIONEN iz nisht geven.

00:19:30.613 --> 00:19:36.715
neyn. SELEKTIONEN nisht, nisht gevezn. ABER m'hot gezogt s'iz do gevezn dort oykhet a krematoryum, nor undz ho'mir nisht gevust.

00:19:37.988 --> 00:19:41.002
un vent zent ir dort bafrayt?

00:19:38.376 --> 00:19:39.399
UNK

00:19:39.827 --> 00:19:42.656
dort zenen mir bafrayt gevorn akhtn may.

00:19:42.831 --> 00:19:43.972
durkh vem?

00:19:43.607 --> 00:19:45.744
durkh rusn zenen mir bafrayt gevorn.

00:19:45.396 --> 00:19:47.448
vos gedenkt ir fun dem tog?

00:19:47.117 --> 00:19:49.861
oh, d- der tog iz gevezn azoy.

00:19:50.003 --> 00:19:52.612
zenen ongekumen di rusn.

00:19:52.770 --> 00:19:59.159
undz ho'mir gemeynt az di yekes forn mit di tanken, mit dem alem. mir hobn dokh gornisht gevust ver dos iz afile.

00:19:59.571 --> 00:20:06.832
hobn mir nisht gevust dem mundir, nisht gor- shpeter oyf a mol zet men epes mentshn loyfn aroys. JEMAND hot shoyn bamerkt az s'iz rusn

00:20:06.832 --> 00:20:08.812
loyfn aroys tsu di drotn

00:20:09.409 --> 00:20:11.664
un zey hobn ongehoybn tsu varfn

00:20:11.704 --> 00:20:14.864
esn, tshokolades un broyt, di yekes

00:20:14.864 --> 00:20:21.624
di rusn. zeyer fayn zenen zey gevezn, di rusn. zeyer, zeyer fayn. dos vos UNK gevezn di andere zayt vos hot moyre gehat far zey

00:20:21.624 --> 00:20:24.557
iz epes andersh, vayl froyen hobn zeyer moyre gehat far zey.

00:20:25.069 --> 00:20:27.889
ABER azoy zenen zey gut gevezn, di rusn.

00:20:27.889 --> 00:20:32.319
un demolt shpeter, nebekh, di ale mentshn vos zenen gevezn krank oyf tifus

00:20:32.339 --> 00:20:39.671
hobn zey SOIGNirt di mentshn, opgekokht supn farshidene. m'hot undz genu- un di mentshn vos hobn gekent, vos zenen nokh gevezn a bisele

00:20:39.671 --> 00:20:40.844
normal

00:20:40.844 --> 00:20:43.687
hot men genumen tsu di kokhn, zol men zey kokhn.

00:20:43.687 --> 00:20:47.425
demolts, mayn mame hot shoyn gearbet. zi hot gearbet bay a kokh, iz dort gevezn

00:20:47.425 --> 00:20:50.173
tsvey ire geshvister kinder hot zi

00:20:51.124 --> 00:20:56.703
UNK m'hot nisht gemegt dort araynkumen tsu di kranke mentshn. hot zi genumen a menashke

00:20:56.929 --> 00:21:03.245
mit a shtrik, un dos hot zi, zey hobn aropgelozt dem shtrik, un azoy hot zi aroyfgeshikt dos esn

00:21:03.245 --> 00:21:04.499
mit dem shtrik.

00:21:05.468 --> 00:21:16.346
un do UNK hot zi geholfn. v- di geshvister, zi hot zikh gefregt "vu iz do JEMAND fun Kroke?" hot men gezogt "do un do iz JEMAND fun Kroke," hot zi geholfn. vemen hot zi gekent hot zi geholfn, di mame.

00:21:16.335 --> 00:21:20.851
un vos iz gevorn mit di oyfzeers? ir hot epes geze-

00:21:19.322 --> 00:21:21.020
zey zenen antlofn.

00:21:21.043 --> 00:21:23.889
zenen antlofn di oyfzeers, di yekes, zenen antlofn.

00:21:24.165 --> 00:21:26.491
m'hot UNK nisht gezen. azoy iz gevorn di

00:21:26.491 --> 00:21:31.300
azoy hot men gezen az di yekes antloyfn, zenen zey oykhet antlofn. di yekes zenen dokh vayter gelofn.

00:21:31.300 --> 00:21:32.901
zenen zey oykhet antlofn.

00:21:33.514 --> 00:21:35.803
bald hot men zey nisht gezen iber hoypt.

00:21:35.961 --> 00:21:38.334
un s'iz geven mentshn vos hobn

00:21:38.475 --> 00:21:43.194
zenen krank gevorn fun dem esn, oder fun d- fun andere zakhn?

00:21:40.770 --> 00:21:44.156
zikher. dos alts, der tifus kumt oykhet fun esn.

00:21:44.331 --> 00:21:49.674
m'hot nisht gehat genug tsu esn. dos iz di krankeyt ⟨kumt⟩ der f- tifus, nisht fun esn un nisht fun zoyberkeyt

00:21:49.748 --> 00:21:52.003
nisht gebodn zikh, nisht gevashn

00:21:52.110 --> 00:21:56.846
d- di, di dos d- hobn gebisn, vi heysn UNK dos d- di loyzn hobn gebisn.

00:21:57.055 --> 00:21:58.905
dos iz dokh shreklekh dos do.

00:21:59.046 --> 00:22:00.322
dos iz shreklekh.

00:21:59.063 --> 00:22:02.820
vi l- vi lang zent ir dort geven in THERESIENSTADT?

00:22:01.932 --> 00:22:04.322
dort ze'mir gevezn ts-

00:22:05.053 --> 00:22:07.244
ershtn zenen mir aroysgeforn

00:22:07.244 --> 00:22:08.912
biz ⟨tsun⟩ akhtn may.

00:22:09.222 --> 00:22:13.418
⟨dem⟩ akhtn may iz gevezn bafrayt di krig, zenen mir nokh geblibn a bisele.

00:22:13.896 --> 00:22:18.952
shpeter, vi lang ken ikh dir nisht zogn genoy. shpeter zenen mir geganen forn keyn

00:22:19.448 --> 00:22:20.471
keyn PRAG.

00:22:21.490 --> 00:22:23.053
shoyn

00:22:23.059 --> 00:22:26.532
shoyn gevezn nokh di krig, nor rusn zenen gevezn oykhet in PRAG

00:22:26.532 --> 00:22:28.785
hot men, ze'mir geganen tsu a JOINT

00:22:28.785 --> 00:22:32.925
hot men undz arayngeleygt in a kaserne, in a groyse kaserne.

00:22:33.117 --> 00:22:36.249
nu, di mame hot bald detsidirt zi fort keyn Poyln

00:22:37.082 --> 00:22:40.521
keyn Poyln, un ikh bin geblibn. zi hot mikh nisht gevolt mitnemen.

00:22:40.521 --> 00:22:42.341
ikh bin geblibn dort

00:22:42.735 --> 00:22:45.018
bin geganen arbetn

00:22:45.018 --> 00:22:50.829
ho- zi hot mikh nisht gevolt lozn in di kaserne aleyn. zi hot moyre gehat mikh aleyn tsu iberlozn in a kaserne

00:22:51.325 --> 00:22:53.749
hot zi mikh gegebn tsu a goye

00:22:53.923 --> 00:22:56.553
un bay di goye hob ikh ges- gevoynt dort

00:22:56.553 --> 00:23:00.473
bay tshekhishe, zeyer fayne mentshn, un ikh hob ⟨zikh⟩ bay zey gearbet a bisele

00:23:00.473 --> 00:23:02.189
un zey hobn mir gegebn tsu esn.

00:23:02.189 --> 00:23:03.671
shpeter

00:23:05.044 --> 00:23:10.320
di dray meydlekh vos zenen undz um- m- tsuzamen eybik geganen in di reye

00:23:10.579 --> 00:23:18.212
zey hobn gezogt, di mame hot gezogt "fort keyn Poyln," un zey hobn gezogt "ikh for nisht keyn Poyln UNK ikh hob nisht vos tsu zukhn in Poyln, iz ikh for keyn Daytshland

00:23:18.212 --> 00:23:20.478
un fun dort ⟨vel ikh⟩ forn keyn Amerike."

00:23:20.704 --> 00:23:23.651
un zenen gekumen keyn FELDAFING

00:23:24.113 --> 00:23:27.330
un zey geyen oyf, in a lager. dos iz gevezn a lager.

00:23:27.454 --> 00:23:29.350
di dray meydlekh.

00:23:28.146 --> 00:23:31.295
di dray meydlekh, un zey geyen oyf di gas

00:23:32.027 --> 00:23:36.425
un di mame hot zi gezogt az "ikh hob a tokhter, zet azoy azoy oys

00:23:36.465 --> 00:23:40.295
efsher t- vestu zi trokh- trefn, efsher lebt zi. past oyf

00:23:40.295 --> 00:23:44.175
oyf dem." zenen geganen oyf di gas, un zey hobn getrofn mayn shvester.

00:23:45.055 --> 00:23:48.376
zey geyen tsu di shvester tsu, un zogn zey "her tsu

00:23:48.376 --> 00:23:53.818
hostu a mame, zi heyst azoy un azoy fil, un hostu a shvester vos heyst zi REGINA?" zogt zi yo.

00:23:53.818 --> 00:23:56.506
"vu zenen zey?" hot zi gezogt "zenen in Tshekhn.

00:23:57.238 --> 00:24:04.201
zenen in Tshekhn," hot zikh oyfgehoybn oyf, oyf, demolts gevezn last vogns, nisht gevezn nokh keyn ⟨tsig⟩, oyf di last vogn

00:24:04.275 --> 00:24:09.264
iz zi gekumen tsu forn keyn Tshekhn. iz zi gekumen dort in JOINT arayn, un zi iz gekumen in di kaserne.

00:24:09.540 --> 00:24:16.672
in kaserne, ikh bin UNK gevezn avek. zi hot zikh ⟨mir⟩ nisht gevust vu ikh bin. ABER yendfal, iz, s'hot gedoyert a bisele, zi hot mikh getrofn.

00:24:17.269 --> 00:24:21.228
un azoy vi zi hot zi mikh getrofn, hot zi gezogt "ikh for tsu di mame keyn Poyln.

00:24:21.707 --> 00:24:26.038
vilst mitforn?" zog ikh "neyn. ikh for n- di mame hot gezogt neyn, ikh for nisht. ikh blayb do"

00:24:26.061 --> 00:24:27.776
un zi iz geforn keyn Poyln.

00:24:28.238 --> 00:24:32.501
un dort hot zikh getrofn mit di mame, un shpeter iz zi gekumen tsurik tsu mir

00:24:33.351 --> 00:24:36.095
un mir, ikh bin gevezn IMMER di BABY.

00:24:36.827 --> 00:24:43.486
tsurik tsu mir iz zi gekumen, un zi hot mikh tsurikgenumen keyn Poyln, ze'mir gevezn in Poyln a tsayt.

00:24:43.459 --> 00:24:45.562
vu zent ir geven i-

00:24:43.628 --> 00:24:47.064
biz, in Kroke. di mame hot gedungen zikh a WO-

00:24:45.687 --> 00:24:50.743
vos hot ir dort tsurik gefunen, fun, di hoyz iz ⟨geshtandlekh⟩, ayer hoyz?

00:24:50.462 --> 00:24:56.345
neyn, dort undzer hoyz hot gevoynt a goye, hobn mir nisht geke- nor mir hobn gedungen a WOHNUNG

00:24:56.605 --> 00:24:58.269
oyf di lange gas

00:24:58.815 --> 00:25:01.289
un di mame hot gehat farmegns UNK

00:25:01.313 --> 00:25:03.815
hot zi gevolt di farmegns zol likvidirn

00:25:03.815 --> 00:25:06.167
un zi hot takesh got zay dank likvidirt.

00:25:05.920 --> 00:25:08.226
zi hot getrofn di farmegns?

00:25:08.248 --> 00:25:09.912
neyn, zi hot gehat hayzer.

00:25:10.392 --> 00:25:12.310
m'hot dos ir tsurikgegebn?

00:25:10.442 --> 00:25:12.059
fun UNK

00:25:12.059 --> 00:25:13.223
hot es farkoyft.

00:25:13.223 --> 00:25:16.106
zi hot dos farko- m'hot ir nisht tsurikgegebn, nor m'hot es farkoyft

00:25:16.365 --> 00:25:19.852
oyf a shpot, ober vifl hot men gegebn iz gevezn UNK

00:25:18.795 --> 00:25:21.556
hot gehat papirn tsu dem?

00:25:20.618 --> 00:25:24.864
yo, vayl zi iz gevezn yorshim. di mentshn zenen nishto, iz zi iz di yoyresh

00:25:24.972 --> 00:25:29.252
gevezn di yoyresh, un eyn papir hot zi gehat ir eygns do, gevezn in Makev

00:25:29.545 --> 00:25:34.247
bin ikh mitgeforn, azoy vi ikh bin stabil geforn keyn Makev, hob ikh zeyer gut gekent Makev

00:25:34.354 --> 00:25:42.785
un di bobe zeydes hobn zey mir gegebn di bobe's pelts mantlen, un der zeyde hot gehat aza pelts oyf, oyfn mantl, kh'veys nisht vos se heyst

00:25:43.045 --> 00:25:51.257
un azoy vi hot mikh keyner nisht gekent, bin gevezn a fremde dort, hot men gegebn tsu a lerer, tsu a lererin tsu trogn di zakhn

00:25:51.921 --> 00:25:57.686
un ikh bin geganen, ikh hob arayngetrogn. ikh bin gekumen keyn Makev nokh di krig mit di mame tsuzamen

00:25:57.878 --> 00:26:02.076
zogt zi, bin ikh geganen tsu di goye, zogt zi UNK "fort avek.

00:26:02.076 --> 00:26:03.879
anisht ruf ikh di politsey."

00:26:04.510 --> 00:26:06.495
iz ze'mir geganen tsu a advokat.

00:26:06.754 --> 00:26:10.142
undz ho'mir bashribn dos o, er hot alts geshribn. undz ze'mir

00:26:10.142 --> 00:26:11.535
untergeshribn

00:26:11.535 --> 00:26:14.291
un er hot gezogt "haynt bay nakht zolstu tsurikforn

00:26:14.601 --> 00:26:16.282
vayl azoy vi di

00:26:16.322 --> 00:26:20.771
di goye veyst az ets zent do, vet zi rufn di N.K.V.D.

00:26:20.895 --> 00:26:24.420
un m'vet kumen enk hargenen," un mir ze'mir bay nakht bald tsurikgeforn.

00:26:25.401 --> 00:26:27.065
azoy zenen gevezn di polyakn.

00:26:27.274 --> 00:26:30.857
un di mentshn vos hobn gevoynt mit aykh

00:26:30.857 --> 00:26:32.702
di areylim

00:26:32.218 --> 00:26:36.667
neyn, zey zenen gut gevezn. zey, di go- vos zey hobn, undz ho'mir

00:26:34.935 --> 00:26:38.354
⟨SO⟩ vos hobn zey gezogt fun di gantse tsushtand?

00:26:39.120 --> 00:26:41.274
⟨veyst⟩ vos hobn zey gezogt?

00:26:39.137 --> 00:26:41.090
vos iz, yo

00:26:41.398 --> 00:26:44.784
oyf poylish zogt men ⟨WSZY JEZYJESZCE⟩?

00:26:44.841 --> 00:26:46.387
"du lebst nokh?"

00:26:47.473 --> 00:26:50.634
farshteyst dos vort? oyf poylish iz dokh andersh oysdrikn

00:26:50.634 --> 00:26:53.052
d- vi eyner zogt "du lebst nokh?"

00:26:55.118 --> 00:26:58.571
s'iz nokh gevezn, dos vos ikh bin geblibn lebn iz nokh gevezn tsu fil

00:26:59.758 --> 00:27:00.984
hobn zey gezogt.

00:27:01.615 --> 00:27:03.853
un ver hot aykh dort geholfn?

00:27:03.910 --> 00:27:05.788
vu? in Poyln?

00:27:04.790 --> 00:27:06.230
in, in Poyln.

00:27:05.788 --> 00:27:11.649
di Poyln iz azoy, leyder, leyder. azoy vi zey kumen keyn Poyln, iz bald ongekumen di papirn fun MAUTHAUSEN

00:27:11.993 --> 00:27:18.951
un iz gekumen di papirn fun ale lager, ver lebt yo, ver lebt, di yekes zenen geven zeyer in ordenung. yedn mentsh hot er ayngeshribn

00:27:18.951 --> 00:27:21.133
vemen m'hot ⟨zey⟩ geleygt in krematoryum arayn

00:27:21.763 --> 00:27:25.380
hot di mame bald getrofn leyder az der tate iz nisht

00:27:25.380 --> 00:27:26.870
nifter gevorn

00:27:27.130 --> 00:27:33.621
un iz gevezn dort, hobn zey oysgerekhnt, es iz a tog for khanike iz di yortsayt fun im.

00:27:34.065 --> 00:27:40.218
demolts iz azoy gevezn. haynt iz shoyn andersh. UNK eybik yednfal me halt mir a tog for khanike yortsayt

00:27:41.085 --> 00:27:46.715
un shpeter iz zi tsurikgekumen a shvester fun di, takesh fun RAVENSBRUCK. zi iz nebekh gevorn

00:27:46.738 --> 00:27:49.452
farvundet oyfn toyte marsh

00:27:49.452 --> 00:27:54.767
mit a, fun a munitsyon fun FLUGZEUG iz arayngefaln UNK do in di hant un di brust

00:27:54.767 --> 00:27:56.384
iz zi gekumen tsu di mame

00:27:56.745 --> 00:28:00.598
un m'hot gevust fun di liste az der shvoger lebt nokh

00:28:00.598 --> 00:28:04.901
azoy hot zi ⟨di⟩ mame bald geshikt, es hot zi oysgeheylt di shvester in shpitol

00:28:04.901 --> 00:28:07.558
un zi hot bald geshikt UNK keyn MAUTHAUSEN

00:28:07.558 --> 00:28:12.146
iz zenen geblibn beyde tsuzamen lebn, got zay dank. zi hot gehat nokh dray kinder nokh di krig.

00:28:12.473 --> 00:28:15.420
un ir hot nisht geklert tsu forn keyn Yisroel?

00:28:15.325 --> 00:28:18.103
undz ho'mir nisht geklert tsu forn

00:28:18.818 --> 00:28:22.206
der frumer oylem hot keyn mol nisht geklert tsu forn keyn Yisroel.

00:28:22.206 --> 00:28:24.600
undz ho'mir geklert tsu forn keyn Amerike.

00:28:25.720 --> 00:28:30.880
yednfals hobn mir gehat a kuzin vos hot undz erleydikt a AFFIDAVIT

00:28:30.880 --> 00:28:35.130
keyn Amerike, fun Amerike ⟨oys⟩ glaykh geshikt a AFFIDAVIT

00:28:35.153 --> 00:28:36.632
nokh keyn Poyln

00:28:37.465 --> 00:28:40.255
ABER s'hot zikh ongehoybn mit di pogromen

00:28:40.255 --> 00:28:44.405
in Poyln iz dokh gevezn pogromen. der ershter pogrom, der tsveyter pogrom, der driter.

00:28:43.287 --> 00:28:46.251
velkhe yor iz dos geven?

00:28:44.535 --> 00:28:47.266
dos iz shoyn gevezn finef un fertsik nokh di krig

00:28:47.266 --> 00:28:49.232
finef iz, finef un fertsik

00:28:49.232 --> 00:28:50.342
gevezn a pogrom.

00:28:50.342 --> 00:28:52.462
iz gevezn in Kroke a pod- -grom.

00:28:52.462 --> 00:28:54.252
ikh bin nisht gevezn derbay.

00:28:54.340 --> 00:29:00.088
mayn mame iz gevezn derbay, ABER ikh bin shpeter gekumen. dos iz gevezn gants fun anfang, shoyn gevezn a pogrom.

00:28:59.166 --> 00:29:01.255
m'vet zikh do opshteln a minut.

00:29:00.730 --> 00:29:01.720
CA VA.
